---
title: Rosemary Garlic Easter Lamb and Red Wine Jus with Smashed Potatoes and Pesto Spring Veg
description: Step into spring with a delicious Easter feast for your Sunday roast. This Rosemary Garlic Easter Lamb and Red Wine Jus offers a luxurious dinner night option, made with premium ingredients for a real taste of luxury at home!
